 scholarship on the ancient Indian past, Professor Chattopadhyaya's latest collection only consolidates his high international reputation.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 4aAsian Studies : India and South Asian Studies. 4aHistory : Intellectual History. 4aLiterature : Literature. 7aHISTORY / Asia / India & South Asia.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143847176140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438471761423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438471761/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles